    The engineering section hums with the sound of backup generators. Warning
    lights flash on multiple consoles. Chief Engineer Tanaka's station is
    abandoned mid-task, diagnostic tools scattered across the deck.

    The engineering computer displays a grim message:

    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │  ENGINEERING SYSTEMS STATUS                                        │
    │  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  │
    │                                                                     │
